      <title>由于消费者支出增加，英国经济增长快于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/uk-economy-grew-faster-than-expected-as-consumers-spent-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济走出衰退，出现两年多来最强劲的增长势头，且增长速度超过此前预期，服务业和消费者支出均比预期强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/uk-economy-grew-faster-than-expected-as-consumers-spent-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
