    <item>
      <title>民主党质疑更换拜登：这可能是可行的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/democrats-question-replacing-biden-here-s-how-it-could-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的辩论表现引发了新的疑问：如果这位 81 岁的总统不再愿意或无法参加竞选，民主党在 11 月是否还有其他选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/democrats-question-replacing-biden-here-s-how-it-could-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:42:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯威胁对黑海上空的美国无人机采取“措施”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/russia-vows-to-take-measures-against-us-drones-over-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部长安德烈·别洛乌索夫指示陆军总参谋部对黑海上空的美国无人机采取“快速反应措施”，因为美国无人机的活动日益频繁，增加了空域发生事件的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/russia-vows-to-take-measures-against-us-drones-over-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷米莱获得大胆经济改革批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-wins-approval-for-landmark-economic-reform-in-argentina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷国会批准了总统哈维尔·米莱伊 (Javier Milei) 提出的亲商改革方案，这标志着这位局外人开始与他一直反对的敌对政治阶层一起执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-wins-approval-for-landmark-economic-reform-in-argentina</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
